name: Natsuki
line: But that doesnt mean you can let me down okay?

name: Natsuki
line: So at least read mine too for now.

name: Natsuki
line: This poem...means a lot to me.

name: Natsuki
line: About as good as yesterdays anyway.

name: Natsuki
line: You gave your poem to Yuri?

name: Natsuki
line: Its not like I wanted to read it anyway.

name: Natsuki
line: Its just pissing me off a little bit that you didnt even think to show me at all.

name: Natsuki
line: Okay...I guess Im going to share my poem with you anyway.

name: Natsuki
line: I really hate that I have to do this.

name: Natsuki
line: But unfortunately I dont have much of a choice.
